---
title: Eggplant Spaghetti “Alla Norma” with Parmesan & Chili Flakes
description: Get ready, farmers market friends—it's eggplant time! For these hearty vegetarian pasta bowls, you’ll slice and fry up tender, savory graffiti eggplant until golden and tender, then toss it with al dente spaghetti in tangy marinara sauce. A sprinkle of nutty shredded Parmesan cheese completes the dish.
